name: cavity filling process
is_a: co:PMD_0020246 ! continous transport
property_value: skos:definition "The process of continuous transport of gas or liquid into the cavity of the solid object, or into otherwise confined place in 3D space (e.g., filling of plasma into the confined magnetic field)." xsd:string

[Term]
