[Term]
id: ACAO:0000103
name: casting mold
is_a: co:PMD_0000075 ! mold
relationship: RO:0000085 ACAO:0000104 ! has function casting mold function

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000104
name: casting mold function
is_a: ACAO:0000101 ! mold function

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000105
name: continuous casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000100 ! casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 197-4:1983(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting fromed by supplying metal continuously to a mould, and withdrawing it continuously from some other part of the mould as it solidifies, the length being independent of the mould dimensions." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000106
name: discrete casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000100 ! casting production process

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000107
name: mold material portion
is_a: co:PMD_0000000 ! Material
property_value: skos:definition "A portion of matter that is part of a casting mold and contributes to the mold’s characteristic material constitution, rather than occurring in or on the mold merely accidentally or incidentally." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000108
name: sand based mold material portion
is_a: ACAO:0000107 ! mold material portion

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000109
name: shell mold
is_a: ACAO:0000135 ! construction specified casting mold
property_value: IAO:0000119 "https://www.britannica.com/technology/shell-mold-casting" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "A mold formed by the shell-molding process, in which resin-coated sand hardens on a heated metal pattern to form thin, strong mold halves that are then assembled." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000110
name: ceramic based mold material portion
is_a: ACAO:0000107 ! mold material portion

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000111
name: plaster based mold material portion
is_a: ACAO:0000107 ! mold material portion

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000112
name: metal based mold material portion
is_a: ACAO:0000107 ! mold material portion

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000113
name: graphite based mold material portion
is_a: ACAO:0000107 ! mold material portion

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000114
name: packed granular mold
is_a: ACAO:0000135 ! construction specified casting mold
property_value: IAO:0000119 "https://www.britannica.com/technology/founding-technology" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "The mold made of materials like sand or clay, that are packed over the face of the pattern (usually made of wood, metal, or resin) to form the cavity into which the molten metal is to be poured. Molds are usually constructed in two halves, and the two halves are joined together once the pattern has been removed from them." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000115
name: casting mold cavity
is_a: co:PMD_0020204 ! pore
relationship: BFO:0000050 ACAO:0000103 ! part of casting mold

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000116
name: split die mold
def: "A clamped die mold composed of separable parts that form the cavity during die casting and are opened after solidification for ejection of the part" []
is_a: ACAO:0000119 ! die mold
property_value: IAO:0000119 "https://www.sciencedirect.com/topics/engineering/die-casting" xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000117
name: continous casting mold
def: "A short water-cooled mold used in continuous casting, through which the forming shell/strand is continuously withdrawn." []
is_a: ACAO:0000135 ! construction specified casting mold
property_value: IAO:0000119 "https://www.britannica.com/technology/steel/Continuous-casting" xsd:string
property_value: skos:altLabel "open-ended mold" xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000118
name: rotating mold
is_a: ACAO:0000135 ! construction specified casting mold
property_value: IAO:0000119 "https://www.britannica.com/technology/iron-processing/The-metal" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "A mold rotated during centrifugal casting so that the melt is shaped while the mold spins." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000119
name: die mold
def: "A casting mold used in die casting, into which the liquid metal is injected." []
is_a: ACAO:0000135 ! construction specified casting mold
property_value: IAO:0000119 "https://www.britannica.com/technology/die-casting" xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000120
name: die casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 23472-1:2020(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting process in which molten metal is injected into a die and held under pressure until complete solidification." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000121
name: permanent mold casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 3522:2007(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting formed in a metal mould, the molten metal being introduced by gravity and solidification under atmospheric pressure." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000122
name: plaster mold casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000132 ! lost foam casting production process

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000123
name: investment casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 19376-1:2025(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting process where waxes are embedded into investment and destroyed during dewaxing and burnout to produce near net shaped metal components." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000124
name: shell mold casting production process
comment: Synthetic resin bonded sand shell mold is a thin shell mold made of mixture of raw sand and resin.
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 23472-1:2020(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting process in which shell mold made of synthetic resin bonded sand is used" xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000125
name: sand casting casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 23472-1:2020(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting process in which sand mold is used and molten metal is poured under the action of gravity." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000126
name: gravity driven continuous casting
is_a: ACAO:0000105 ! continuous casting production process

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000127
name: pressure driven continuous casting
is_a: ACAO:0000105 ! continuous casting production process

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000128
name: centrifugal casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 23472-1:2020(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Casting process in which molten metal is filled into a mold that rotates around a horizontal or vertical axis and solidifies under the action of centrifugal force to produce castings." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000129
name: vertical gravity driven continuous casting
is_a: ACAO:0000126 ! gravity driven continuous casting

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000130
name: horizontal gravity driven continuous casting
is_a: ACAO:0000126 ! gravity driven continuous casting

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000131
name: pressure die casting production process
is_a: ACAO:0000120 ! die casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 28401:2024(en)" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "Die casting where the molten metal is introduced under high pressure." xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000132
name: lost foam casting production process
def: "Casting process which uses expendable pattern for molding. When pouring, high temperature molten metal causes the pattern to burn, gasify and disappear, and fills up the cavity occupied by the pattern at the same time." []
is_a: ACAO:0000106 ! discrete casting production process
property_value: IAO:0000119 "ISO 23472-1:2020(en)" xsd:string

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000133
name: casting mold filling process
is_a: ACAO:0000028 ! cavity filling process
is_a: ACAO:0000134 ! liquid transport of metal
intersection_of: ACAO:0000134 ! liquid transport of metal
intersection_of: BFO:0000066 ACAO:0000115 ! occurs in casting mold cavity
relationship: BFO:0000066 ACAO:0000115 ! occurs in casting mold cavity

[Term]
id: ACAO:0000134
name: liquid transport of metal
is_a: ACAO:0000027 ! liquid transport
intersection_of: ACAO:0000027 ! liquid transport
intersection_of: RO:0000057 co:PMD_0000852 ! has participant metal
relationship: RO:0000057 co:PMD_0000852 ! has participant metal

