[Term]
id: co:PMD_0060009
name: specification datum
comment: The intent of the specification datum is to express the "Sollwert" of some qualitiy or behavioral material property. Then, the specification datum can be further specified by  some value specification.
is_a: IAO:0000033 ! directive information entity
property_value: co:PMD_0000060 "true" xsd:boolean
property_value: skos:definition "A directive information entity that provides information of a setpoint of some value, i.e., it is an intended value." xsd:string
property_value: skos:example "The setpoint value of a ultimate tensile strength of some steel material" xsd:string

[Term]
id: co:PMD_0090000
name: semiconductor
is_a: co:PMD_0000000 ! Material
relationship: RO:0000086 co:PMD_0090002 ! has quality band gap
relationship: RO:0000091 co:PMD_0090001 ! has disposition semiconductivity
property_value: co:PMD_0000060 "true" xsd:boolean
property_value: skos:definition "A semiconductor is an engineered material representing a class of materials characterized by an electrical conductivity between that of a conductor and an insulator. This is a result of a range of inexistent energy states in ther electron configuration between the valence and conduction band (bandgap)." xsd:string

[Term]
id: co:PMD_0090001
name: semiconductivity
is_a: co:PMD_0000005 ! material property
property_value: co:PMD_0000060 "true" xsd:boolean
property_value: skos:definition "Semiconductivity is the disposition of a material to conduct electricity only when a certain level of excitation (via temperature, impurities, photonic excitation, electric field) elevates electrons from the valence band into the conduction band." xsd:string

[Term]
id: co:PMD_0090002
name: band gap
is_a: co:PMD_0020142 ! energy
property_value: skos:altLabel "bandgap" xsd:string
property_value: skos:altLabel "energy gap" xsd:string
property_value: skos:definition "A bandgap is an energy range between the valence band and the conduction band in a solid where no electronic states exist." xsd:string
property_value: skos:example "Silicon has a band gap of 1.107 eV at room temperature." xsd:string

